column5: Probably doesn't weigh anymore than a typical yammy 4 stroke

You lost some weight Dave. I saw a custom bike in town that was heading to Friday the 13th bike rally in Port Dover. A full blown V8 pushing 500 HP. That's what I really want, to straddle 500 horse at 7000 RPM mere inches from my future legacies. Heck Hugh Hefner had kids in his late 70's. Hold on Nelly!
